OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be largely dry. Clouding over in
OL,7,Fthe early hours with a little rain
OL,8,Fpossible later in the night. Fresh
OL,9,Foccasionally strong southwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FShetland rather cloudy at
OL,13,Ffirst with some showery rain.
OL,14,FOtherwise dry with a few sunny spells.
OL,15,FFresh southwesterly winds easing in
OL,16,Fthe afternoon.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMainly
OL,19,Fdry on Tuesday and Wednesday, perhaps
OL,20,Fthe odd shower. Rain spreading east on
OL,21,FThursday, drier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
